    <stitle>FRAME - REPAIR AND REINFORCEMENT RECOMMENDED PROCEDURES</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcsubsec id="x0100101">
        <title>REPAIR AND REINFORCEMENT RECOMMENDED PROCEDURES</title>
        <svcsubsecinfo>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>In some cases of frame damage, the sidemembers must be replaced rather than repaired. Examples
                        of this are:
                    </para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
            <seqlist>
                <item>
                    <para>When sidemember cracks caused complete separation or a visible deformation of the section.
                    </para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>When the sidemembers are extensively deformed. Consult with your field service representative
                        and frame repair specialists if in doubt.
                    </para>
                </item>
            </seqlist>
        </svcsubsecinfo>
    </svcsubsec>
